Yemen Forces Open Fire on Protesters, Killing One, Mansour Says

-- B y   D o n n a   A b u - N a s r
-- 
2011-04-30T10:01:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-30/yemen-forces-open-fire-on-protesters-killing-one-mansour-says.html
Yemeni security forces in tanks and
armored vehicles opened fire on protesters in Aden, killing one
person and wounding scores of others, Yemeni journalist Anis
Mansour told Al-Jazeera Television from the scene.  The casualties were hit in the head and the upper body,
said Mansour. Bursts of gunfire could be heard as he spoke.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Donna Abu-Nasr at   dabunasr@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net . 